1. sudo gedit /usr/share/applications/eclipse.desktop 

2.在上述文件中添加如下内容
[Desktop Entry]
Encoding=UTF-8
Name=eclipse
Comment=Eclipse IDE
Exec=/home/oops/program_files/eclipse/eclipse
Icon=/home/oops/program_files/eclipse/icon.xpm
Terminal=false
StartupNotify=true
Type=Application
Categories=Application;Development;

3.chmod u+x eclipse.desktop

4.
desktop-file-install --add-category Development eclipse.desktop

